@page "/"
@page "/home"

<PageTitle>Home - Welcome</PageTitle>

<div class="home-container">
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1 class="hero-title">Transform Your Business with Innovation</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">Catalyst Software Solutions develops tailored software solutions that optimize workflows and support business growth. Our team also specializes in modernizing legacy applications—enhancing performance, security, and scalability across your entire technology stack.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
                <a href="/services" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="challenges-section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Are You Experiencing These Software Challenges?</h2>
            <p>Many businesses struggle with technology that holds them back rather than moving them forward</p>
        </div>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card challenge-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                        <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"></line>
                        <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"></line>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Outdated Legacy Systems?</h3>
                <p>Are you stuck with old, slow software that's expensive to maintain and impossible to integrate with modern tools?</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card challenge-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"></path>
                        <line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"></line>
                        <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"></line>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>One-Size-Fits-All Software?</h3>
                <p>Does your current software force you to change your processes instead of adapting to your unique business needs?</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card challenge-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                        <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"></line>
                        <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"></line>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Manual Processes & Inefficiency?</h3>
                <p>Are your teams wasting time on repetitive tasks that could be automated, reducing productivity and increasing errors?</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card challenge-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path>
                        <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"></polyline>
                        <line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Integration Nightmares?</h3>
                <p>Struggling to connect your various systems, leading to data silos and disconnected workflows across your organization?</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card challenge-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
                        <path d="M12 8v4"></path>
                        <path d="M12 16h.01"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Security & Compliance Concerns?</h3>
                <p>Are you worried about data breaches, outdated security measures, or meeting industry compliance requirements?</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card challenge-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M3 3v18h18"></path>
                        <path d="M18.7 8l-5.1 5.2-2.8-2.7L7 14.3"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Scaling Limitations?</h3>
                <p>Is your current software preventing growth? Does it crash under load or fail to handle increased demand?</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="challenges-cta">
            <p>If any of these sound familiar, we can help. Our custom solutions are designed to solve your specific challenges.</p>
            <a href="/consultation" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Free Consultation</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features-section">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>
            <p>Delivering value through expertise, innovation, and commitment</p>
        </div>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"></path>
                        <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"></path>
                        <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Scalable Solutions</h3>
                <p>Build with confidence knowing our solutions grow alongside your business needs and ambitions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                        <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Fast Delivery</h3>
                <p>Experience rapid implementation without compromising on quality or attention to detail.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
                        <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Proven Results</h3>
                <p>Join hundreds of satisfied clients who have achieved measurable success with our services.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stats-section">
        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">500+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Projects Delivered</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">98%</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Client Satisfaction</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">24/7</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Support Available</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">15+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Years Experience</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="cta-content">
            <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
            <p>Let's discuss how we can help transform your business and achieve your goals together.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-light">Contact Us Today</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<style>
    .home-container {
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .hero-section {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F26A2C 0%, #1F6FB2 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 120px 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-content {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero-title {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        opacity: 0.95;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 16px;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
        padding: 14px 32px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        display: inline-block;
        border: 2px solid transparent;
    }

    .btn-primary {
        background: white;
        color: #F26A2C;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        background: #F7F9FC;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
        background: transparent;
        color: white;
        border-color: white;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
        background: white;
        color: #F26A2C;
    }

    .btn-light {
        background: var(--bg-white);
        color: var(--primary-orange);
    }

    .btn-light:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .challenges-section {
        padding: 80px 20px;
        background: var(--bg-white);
    }

    .challenges-section .section-header {
        max-width: 800px;
    }

    .challenge-card {
        border-left: 4px solid var(--catalyst-red);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .challenge-card:hover {
        border-left-color: var(--catalyst-orange);
        transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .challenge-card .feature-icon {
        color: var(--catalyst-red);
    }

    .challenge-card:hover .feature-icon {
        color: var(--catalyst-orange);
    }

    .challenges-cta {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 60px auto 0;
        padding: 40px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(242, 106, 44, 0.08) 0%, rgba(31, 111, 178, 0.08) 100%);
        border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .challenges-cta p {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .features-section {
        padding: 80px 20px;
        background: var(--bg-light);
    }

    .section-header {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto 60px;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .section-header p {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        color: #718096;
    }

    .features-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 32px;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .feature-card {
        background: var(--bg-white);
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    }

    .feature-icon {
        color: var(--catalyst-blue);
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--deep-navy);
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .feature-card p {
        color: #718096;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .stats-section {
        padding: 80px 20px;
        background: var(--bg-white);
    }

    .stats-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 40px;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .stat-item {
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .stat-number {
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--catalyst-orange);
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .stat-label {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #718096;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .cta-section {
        background: var(--gradient-primary);
        color: var(--text-white);
        padding: 80px 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .cta-content {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .cta-content h2 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .cta-content p {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        opacity: 0.95;
    }

    @@media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
        }

        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .cta-content h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
    }
</style>
